                     <interp inst="t18471213-397-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>, stealing 6 sovereigns, 4 half-crowns, 2 shillings, and 2 pence; the moneys of <persName id="t18471213-name-751" type="victimName">
